eu.cqse.check.framework.util.clike

Class ConditionalBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.cqse.check.framework.util.clike.ConditionalBlock

  • public class ConditionalBlock
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a single block of a conditional expression. It can be one of the types of EConditionalType. An condition may be given if the block represents an if, else if or case block. The content of the block is a list of shallow entities that represent the code that gets executed when the block gets executed.
